(firstQuint)Comparison of Pharmacokinetics of Infacort Versus Immediate-release Hydrocortisone.

 This was a single centre, open-label, randomised, 5-way crossover study design to compare the PK of Infacort(R) versus immediate-release hydrocortisone tablets and to evaluate the dose proportionality of 0.

5 mg, 2 mg, 5 mg and 10 mg Infacort(R).

 The study was conducted in 1 cohort of 16 healthy male subjects and comprised a Screening Visit, 5 treatment periods (Treatment Periods 1 to 5) and a Post-study Visit.

